The 'Life' pages contain the lineage and a hierarchal view of all the taxonomic names 
in HOMD. Each name is a link to a new life page in that lineage. To get back to the beginning
select the 'Cellular Organisms' link at the top of the hierarchy.

On many of the pages there is additional information about the focus rank-name. For instance
