In each rank row there is a link: 'Abundance' that opens the <a href='/help/help-page?pagecode=taxon/ecology'>ecology (abundance) page</a> for that
taxonomic name. 

Once you are at the genus level you are presented with the HMTs (human microbial taxa) that
are in that genus. The HMT links now take you to the taxon description page for that HMT.
